# UPC implementation

## Servers:

- HTTP server
  - Functionality
    - Accept channel opening tx
      - How to integrate with arbitrary other bank systems?
    - Accept channel update tx (close)
      - How to integrate with arbitrary other bank systems?
    - HTTP display of channel status: easy
    - Evaluate conditions
      - Gas?
        - Built in conditions at first

- Blockchain server
  - Functionality
    - Accept channel opening tx
    - Accept channel update tx (close)
    - Respond to channel status queries

## Clients

- Routing peer
  - Speak routing algorithm
  - Interface to human or other decisionmaker on fee acceptability
